{"tid":2228854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美重啟冷戰政策 禁共產黨員申綠卡  羅冠聰：劍指中共","createTime":"2020-10-04T02:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T03:34:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d195101fc6e29af116aa02a5285bb09435fdee5f","tid":2228854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:41:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/SHSNE42QTVABRBVO3EW5JAGACE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FSHSNE42QTVABRBVO3EW5JAGACE%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=d2025263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FSHSNE42QTVABRBVO3EW5JAGACE%2F&h=feb5de81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/SHSNE42QTVABRBVO3EW5JAGACE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美重啟冷戰政策 禁共產黨員申綠卡 <br />\n羅冠聰：劍指中共<br />\n<br />\n美媒早前報道，美國正考慮推出針對中共黨員的簽證禁令，在禁令未推出之際，美國移民局周五官網更新一項政策指引，提到除非經過特別允許，曾經加入或隸屬共產黨或其他極權主義政黨的人士，申請綠卡都將不獲受理。美國移民顧問鄭存柱指出，美國法律以往已寫明共產黨員是不符合移民美國原因之一，此次公告「說明今後會嚴格一點處理這類移民」。前香港眾志主席羅冠聰認為該指引是「劍指中共」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「中共不等於中國」嚴格區別黨員人民<br />\n<br />\n美國公民及移民服務局（USCIS）周五（2日）新發佈一項政策指南，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5M-4dV7B-yUgRbNTLg2WgC3vJ0U=/2025x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MTGQRWNHNVHOXLUQRNTUCLP4LQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5M-4dV7B-yUgRbNTLg2WgC3vJ0U%3D%2F2025x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMTGQRWNHNVHOXLUQRNTUCLP4LQ.jpg&h=4dd1bfff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美移民局更新指引，禁曾加入或隸屬共產黨人士申請綠卡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉銳紹︰比以前「揸得緊」<br />\n<br />\n不過值得關注的是，此項政策並非新政策，美國移民法例禁止共產黨員移民，1990年受冷戰結束影響，放寬了禁止共產黨員移民入境及移民的有關規定。此次公告只是針對在美國申請綠卡的人士，例如人在美國的共產黨員，申請綠卡時可能不會通過申請。至於旅遊、商務等非移民簽證則不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，是否加入共產黨是移民官面試的問題之一，但過去面試者給予否定答案，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在明尼蘇達州執業的律師周東發表示，移民局去年已開始默默操作這項政策，。。。。。。。。。。「回答『是』可能直接被拒，回答『不是』涉嫌詐欺」，民眾最好謹慎作答。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「為生計」入黨可豁免<br />\n<br />\n至於指南中提到的「例外」狀況，周東發指，包括有迫不得已成為黨員、法律規定工作必須加入共產黨、年少加入共青團但之後退出等。一般最常見的例外情況，是「為了生計與生存，不得不加入共產黨」，或是申請移民至少前五年已退黨。<br />\n<br />\n中美對立近年加劇，美國《紐約時報》今年7月曾報道，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國移民局/《世界日報》/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aAzIMnTP5CI3wWL6sS-mxaYCcfw=/969x406/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D2FEDZJE4NHXNPI7T7SYAKX3XE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaAzIMnTP5CI3wWL6sS-mxaYCcfw%3D%2F969x406%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD2FEDZJE4NHXNPI7T7SYAKX3XE.gif&h=428c106d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e6aeb95007c46f36075db37026350ebebe964c4","tid":2228854,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">當日可以為生計入得鬼党，擔保以後唔會？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，寫文毒果記者／蚑底聰可唔可以唔好再用&quot;劍指&quot;呢類蝗文化僭洗港腦呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？</span></span></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"440e25d5275e721e118f1c90cc614103b8372bee","tid":2228854,"uid":2290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">美移民局更新指引，禁曾加入或隸屬共產黨人士申請綠卡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想退黨保平安都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}